<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-55-1304 </DOCNO><TEXT>A low cost and easy to use electronic system for photovoltaic solar panellingvalidation is described. It measures, with a certain periodicity, voltageand current given by the panel, determines the supplied power, and everyso often, its maximum values. The unit is fitted with a data storagesystem which allows data recording for later analysis. (Author)</TEXT></DOC>